<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
  <title>operator manual — zeroday</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@300;400;500;600&family=VT323&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/admin.css" />
</head>
<body>
<div class="crt-stage">
  <div class="app-shell">
    <header class="opsbar">
      <div class="brand">
        <span class="brand-mark"></span>
        <span>zeroday · operator manual</span>
      </div>
      <div class="center">
        <div class="seg"><span>document</span><b>v3.14.2</b></div>
        <div class="seg"><span>classification</span><b>operators only</b></div>
      </div>
      <div class="right">
        <a class="btn sm" href="/" style="text-decoration:none">[ ← back ]</a>
      </div>
    </header>
    <div style="flex:1;overflow:auto;padding:40px 60px;max-width:840px;margin:0 auto;width:100%">
      <div style="font-size:9.5px;letter-spacing:0.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--phosphor-faint);margin-bottom:8px">operator manual · v3.14.2</div>
      <h1 class="chrome glow-strong" style="font-size:28px;letter-spacing:0.02em;margin:0 0 28px;font-weight:500">so you got the email.</h1>

      <div class="drawer-section" style="margin-bottom:22px">
        <h4 style="margin:0 0 8px;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--phosphor-dim)">// preamble</h4>
        <div style="font-size:13.5px;line-height:1.75;color:var(--phosphor-dim);letter-spacing:0.01em">
          welcome to <span class="chrome">zeroday</span>. you are one of <span class="chrome">eighteen</span>. you got here because someone vouched for you · a real person, not a form. don't make them regret it.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="drawer-section" style="margin-bottom:22px">
        <h4 style="margin:0 0 8px;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--phosphor-dim)">01 // what this is</h4>
        <div style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.75;color:var(--phosphor-dim)">
          nineteen trials · one cohort · one shot. each trial drops a flag in the shape <span class="chrome">ZERODAY{...}</span>. clear it, the next one opens. order is enforced · don't try to skip ahead, the server won't take it.
          <br/><br/>the last seven days the gibson is <span class="chrome">hot</span>. that's where the real points live. survive that long and you make the wall.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="drawer-section" style="margin-bottom:22px">
        <h4 style="margin:0 0 8px;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--phosphor-dim)">02 // your handle</h4>
        <div style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.75;color:var(--phosphor-dim)">
          you picked it on the way in. you keep it. it's how the leaderboard knows you · it's how the others know you. <span class="chrome">no one</span>, including the admin, sees your real name from inside the game.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="drawer-section" style="margin-bottom:22px">
        <h4 style="margin:0 0 8px;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--phosphor-dim)">03 // hints</h4>
        <div style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.75;color:var(--phosphor-dim)">
          stuck for too long, an operator may push you a hint. five flavors, escalating:
          <br/><span class="chrome">L1</span> · nudge · costs you 1 pt
          <br/><span class="chrome">L2</span> · direction · costs you 2 pts
          <br/><span class="chrome">L3</span> · technique · costs you 4 pts
          <br/><span class="chrome">L4</span> · strong · costs you 7 pts
          <br/><span class="chrome">L5</span> · spoiler · costs you 10 pts
          <br/><br/>you can refuse. you cannot un-refuse. <span class="amber">the gibson respects struggle.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="drawer-section" style="margin-bottom:22px">
        <h4 style="margin:0 0 8px;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--phosphor-dim)">04 // your two invites</h4>
        <div style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.75;color:var(--phosphor-dim)">
          you can pull two more in. that's the whole budget. tokens are signed, locked to the inbox, dead in 72h. choose well · the cohort is the game.
          <br/><br/>need a third? ask the admin · if it's a good story, it gets through.
          <br/><span class="dim" style="font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.06em">(use the slot panel in the lobby · revoke or expiry frees a slot.)</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="drawer-section" style="margin-bottom:22px">
        <h4 style="margin:0 0 8px;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--phosphor-dim)">05 // etiquette</h4>
        <div style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.75;color:var(--phosphor-dim)">
          · don't share flags. it's logged · we will know.<br/>
          · don't dos the box. <span class="warn">it's a shared hairpin · break it for one, break it for everyone.</span><br/>
          · ask in <span class="chrome">slack#zeroday-ops</span>. talk in metaphor.<br/>
          · when you finish a trial, write the rest of us a <span class="chrome">/postmortem</span> · everyone learns.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="border-top:1px solid var(--rule);padding-top:18px;margin-top:24px;text-align:center">
        <div style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.75;color:var(--phosphor);letter-spacing:0.04em;font-style:italic">
          "the gibson doesn't care if you're tired."<br/>
          <span class="dim" style="font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.16em;text-transform:uppercase;font-style:normal">— previous cohort · final transmission</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-top:36px;display:flex;gap:10px;justify-content:flex-end;align-items:center">
        <span class="dim" style="font-size:10.5px;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-right:auto">this manual lives at <span class="chrome">/manual</span> · reread it before you submit</span>
        <a class="btn sm amber solid" href="/" style="text-decoration:none">[ understood ▸ ]</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
